The horse girls are waiting 
at their gates, ready to go.

00:17:38.810 --> 00:17:42.020
Last up is Tokai Teio, and she seems calm.

00:17:42.020 --> 00:17:44.390
She walks up to the gate with an 
expression that conveys confidence.

00:17:44.750 --> 00:17:49.510
Winning this race, she would earn her second crown 
while undefeated after the Satsukishou,

00:17:49.510 --> 00:17:51.900
