You should give her some 
pointers on her start.

00:18:05.680 --> 00:18:06.620
Put a sock in it.

00:18:06.980 --> 00:18:11.520
The horse girls are staying close to the 
center as they approach the first turn.

00:18:11.520 --> 00:18:14.780
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven...

00:18:14.780 --> 00:18:16.910
Tokai Teio is in eighth place, 
eighth place and on the outside

00:18:16.910 --> 00:18:18.500
as they enter the first turn.

00:18:18.950 --> 00:18:20.180
Eighth place...

00:18:20.180 --> 00:18:24.310
I'll have to run on the outside, 
but that'll let me get a feel for the others!

00:18:24.310 --> 00:18:25.600
I can do this!

00:18:25.600 --> 00:18:28.640
Watch me, Prez!

00:18:29.690 --> 00:18:32.460
Looks like starting on the outside 
hasn't been much of a problem.

00:18:32.980 --> 00:18:37.990
Do you remember what you told 
Teio long ago, Maruzensky?

00:18:37.990 --> 00:18:41.870
To be like Rudolf-chan, you're going 
to need talent, effort, and luck.

00:18:41.870 --> 00:18:44.430
And you can't afford to miss a single one.

00:18:44.430 --> 00:18:45.660
Keep that in mind.

00:18:45.660 --> 00:18:47.380
Yes, of course.

00:18:47.380 --> 00:18:52.380
Teio's naturally flexible knees 
and ankles give her talent.

00:18:52.920 --> 00:18:55.500
And she's put in more effort 
than anyone else, every day.

00:18:56.460 --> 00:18:58.030
That leaves luck.

00:18:58.030 --> 00:19:02.560
Well, they do say that the luckiest 
horse girls tend to win the Derby.

00:19:02.560 --> 00:19:06.310
You could almost say today's 
race is a test of Teio's luck.

00:19:07.390 --> 00:19:08.550
Teio-san...

00:19:10.090 --> 00:19:12.170
They're approaching the third 
turn from the backstretch,

00:19:12.170 --> 00:19:14.480
with Tokai Teio in seventh 
place on the outside.

00:19:14.480 --> 00:19:17.420
Teio's being forced to run on the outside.

00:19:17.420 --> 00:19:18.850
It's okay!

00:19:19.550 --> 00:19:22.780
Don't you think that the outside is 
easier to run on in a straightaway?

00:19:22.780 --> 00:19:24.990
There's no crowding, and the 
turf is in better shape.

00:19:24.990 --> 00:19:27.580
She'll zip past them all in the last stretch!

00:19:28.590 --> 00:19:29.880
They're rounding the fourth turn!

00:19:29.880 --> 00:19:32.460
Tokai Teio has moved up through 
sixth and fifth place!

00:19:37.170 --> 00:19:39.840
No one in front me. All right!

00:19:39.840 --> 00:19:40.550
Whoa!

00:19:40.550 --> 00:19:44.510
Tokai Teio, here I go!

00:19:44.510 --> 00:19:46.220
Tokai Teio is going hard in the last spurt!

00:19:46.220 --> 00:19:49.860
Tokai Teio, moving up on the outside!
 She's climbing fast!

00:19:50.730 --> 00:19:51.770
I can't!

00:19:51.460 --> 00:19:54.260
With four hundred meters to go,
 Tokai Teio pushes through!

00:19:51.770 --> 00:19:52.840
I can't!

00:19:52.840 --> 00:19:53.730
I can't!

00:19:54.260 --> 00:19:55.360
She's made it to the top!

00:19:55.360 --> 00:19:57.440
But there are other horse girls on her tail!

00:19:57.440 --> 00:19:58.790
Wow, impressive!

00:19:58.790 --> 00:20:00.940
She'll feel like she's flying now.

00:20:00.940 --> 00:20:02.180
And Tokai Teio breaks away!

00:20:02.180 --> 00:20:03.460
Tokai Teio is clear!

00:20:03.460 --> 00:20:04.950
Tokai Teio is still clear!

00:20:04.950 --> 00:20:06.120
She's three lengths ahead! Now four!

00:20:06.120 --> 00:20:08.410
There's no questioning it! Not anymore!

00:20:08.410 --> 00:20:10.170
Starting on the outside hasn't 
been any problem for her!

00:20:10.170 --> 00:20:12.130
Tokai Teio blazes onward!

00:20:10.400 --> 00:20:11.830
Go!

00:20:12.130 --> 00:20:16.280
And Tokai Teio... has won the Japanese Derby!

00:20:14.830 --> 00:20:15.540
Japanese Derby

00:20:16.280 --> 00:20:18.720
She obtains her Double Crown!

00:20:18.720 --> 00:20:21.050
This was an absolute blowout!

00:20:21.050 --> 00:20:24.310
Tokai Teio wins the Japanese Derby,

00:20:24.310 --> 00:20:29.180
becoming the first undefeated Double 
Crown winner since Symboli Rudolf!

00:20:29.180 --> 00:20:30.280
She did it!

00:20:34.680 --> 00:20:39.230
Teio! Teio! Teio!

00:20:36.730 --> 00:20:41.230
And they're calling her name! 
The crowd is calling for Teio!

00:20:39.230 --> 00:20:50.250
Teio! Teio! Teio!

00:20:56.620 --> 00:20:59.150
Teio might have just outdone the Emperor.

00:20:59.150 --> 00:21:01.460
I guess prodigies really do exist,
as frustrating as that might be.

00:21:04.470 --> 00:21:06.670
Nicely done. Con—

00:21:05.940 --> 00:21:09.100
Save the congratulations for 
after she wins the Kikkasho.

00:21:09.100 --> 00:21:12.240
She still hasn't accomplished 
her goal, after all.

00:21:27.070 --> 00:21:30.390
It's time for the Winning Concert, 
where the brightest horse girls get to shine!

00:21:30.390 --> 00:21:34.150
And in the center position is the undefeated 
victor of the Derby, Tokai Teio!

00:21:34.150 --> 00:21:35.820
We might be looking at the first

00:21:35.820 --> 00:21:38.710
undefeated Triple Crown winner 
since Symboli Rudolf.

00:21:55.900 --> 00:22:00.900
The impulse that races through 
me at the speed of light

00:22:00.900 --> 00:22:05.820
is the determination to make my 
wish come true, no matter what it costs!

00:22:05.820 --> 00:22:07.780
(No fear)

00:22:06.810 --> 00:22:08.320
It's once in a lifetime

00:22:08.320 --> 00:22:09.320
(Trust you)

00:22:09.320 --> 00:22:10.820
And in this moment

00:22:10.820 --> 00:22:12.650
I'm gonna bet it all

00:22:12.650 --> 00:22:15.660
Believing in myself!

00:22:15.660 --> 00:22:20.540
If luck is what you really need sometimes

00:22:20.540 --> 00:22:27.740
I'll find a way to make the 
melody of fate play my number

